# 🔹 Lambda Expression

## ✅ Definition

A **lambda expression** is a short way to write **anonymous functions**

---

## 💻 Syntax

```java
(parameters) -> expression
```

---

## 💻 Example

```java
interface Test {
    void show();
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        Test t = () -> System.out.println("Hello Lambda");

        t.show();
    }
}
```

---

## 🎯 Why Lambda?

* Less code
* Functional programming
* Used in streams

---

# 🔥 Interview Q&A

