# 🧠 5️⃣ MEMORY MANAGEMENT (VERY IMPORTANT 🔥🔥🔥)

---

# 🔹 Stack vs Heap

| Stack            | Heap            |
| ---------------- | --------------- |
| Stores variables | Stores objects  |
| Fast             | Slower          |
| Thread-safe      | Not thread-safe |

---

## 💻 Example

```java
int a = 10;         // stack
String s = "Java";  // heap
```

